http://www.html5rocks.com/en/tutorials/offline/storage/

Cache manifest
- Problems: if any of the resources is missing all the cache is not valid and will not be downloaded


Supported Browser
- Web SQL Database: http://caniuse.com/sql-storage
- Index DB : http://caniuse.com/#search=indexdb
- File API : http://caniuse.com/#search=file api


Comments:
WebSQL
 * Not optimized DB, seek take a long time for many records.
 * Safari is asking for permission if more space is require. Fail to store data if there is no space, we need to have a workaround for that.
   I manged to get up tp 1GB of local file system :-)


